that the Japanese police have
created to avoid confusion.

55
00:04:16,840 --> 00:04:18,341
L is dead.

56
00:04:19,092 --> 00:04:23,597
Director Mason... Who is he?

57
00:04:24,055 --> 00:04:25,098
Well...

58
00:04:25,348 --> 00:04:29,728
He is, let's just say...
he's L's true successor.

59
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:32,856
